item.description: cdsctl project group import Import group linked to a CDS project Synopsis Import group linked to a CDS project cdsctl project group import PROJECT-KEY PATH [flags] Options --force Use force flag to replace groups in your project -h, --help help for import Options inherited from parent commands -f, --file string set configuration file -k, --insecure (SSL) This option explicitly allows curl to perform "insecure" SSL connections and transfers.
